settings.description: A remake of the first half of Donut Plains 3 from Super Mario World. I made this just to get a hang on what this editor can do. Level design credit goes to the original creators at Nintendo.
Underground bunker as well as a bolt tower. A bolt tower is a tower that uses bolt platforms. Enjoy.
